Daily Trust reporter, Musa Abdullahi Krishi, has been abducted by armed policemen at the National Assembly complex. The whereabout of Mr. Krishi is still unknown and there are fears that he may be in danger. Efforts to reach him have proved abortive as all his phone lines are switched off. The Police authority, who has been on the trail of Mr. Krishi, has failed to inform Daily Trust on why the fearless journalist was abducted by armed policemen.   Detail later.....